headline: Alphatec (ATEC) Beats Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates

headline: STERIS (STE) Announces 20th Year of Dividend Growth with US$0.63 Per Share
summary: STERIS (STE) has seen a recent quarter price increase of 3%, potentially influenced by its announcement of a dividend increase to $0.63 per share, marking its 20th consecutive year of dividend growth. This strong dividend performance underscores the company's commitment to shareholder value. Despite executive changes and being dropped from the Russell 1000 Dynamic Index, STERIS's move aligns with robust earnings reports from major tech corporations, contributing to positive market sentiment...
